</head>

<body>
    <div class="top-header">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row top-row">
                <div class="col-xs-6">
                    <div class="top" id="top-lf">
                        <a href="/" class="nav-link text-white">
                            Home
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-6">
                    <div class="top" id="top-mid">
                        <a href="/signup" class="nav-link text-white">
                            Sign Up
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-6">
                    <div class="top" id="top-rt">
                        <a href="/event-info" class="nav-link text-white">
                            Details
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row s-row">

    </div>

    <div class="row trd-row">
        <div class="col-10">
            <div class="row" id="event-description">
                <p>
                    With the end of Bootcamp just around the corner, it's time we start not <em>only</em> developing
                    our "Web Dev" skills, but also our "Net Dev" connections!
                </p>
                <p>
                    So. . . let's hang outside of class to talk life, code, hobbies, and dreams so we are aware of
                    how to help each other progress, regardless of how careers unfold! Strong networks consist of
                    people with a diverse set of skills, strengths and industry knowledge.
                </p>
                
                <span class="accent">What to Bring?</span> 
                <br>
                <br>
                Your badass self and some food to share! 
                <br>
                Please sign up below!
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="row" id="event-details-heading">
                <h3>
                    <span class="bg-text">#NetDev</span>
                </h3>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row ffth-row">
        <div class="container col-1" id="signup-heading">
            <div class="row" id="sign-up">
                <h1>
                    <span class="signup-bg-text">Sign up</span>
                </h1>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container col-3" id="form-container">
            <div class="row" id="form-row">
                <form>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control " id="first-name" placeholder="First Name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="last-name" placeholder="Last Name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="item" placeholder="What food/drink will you bring?">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <button type="submit" id='submit' class="btn">Sign up!</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
                <p id='error-message' class='text-danger' style='display:none'>Please fill out all fields</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-7">
            <div class="row" id="attendees">
                {{{body}}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row frth-row">
        <div class="col-4 details">
                <div class="row" id="event-details">
                <div class="col">
                <h6>
                    <span class="accent">Details</span>
                    <br>
                    Saturday, 4/20/2019
                    <br>
                    3:00pm - 6:00pm (right after class!) 
                    <br>
                    745 18th Street, Santa Monica, CA 90402 
                </h6>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6 map">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/350" alt="placeholder map">
        </div>
        <div class="col-1">
            <div class="row" id="event-details-heading">
                <h3>
                    <span class="address-bg-text">Address</span>
                </h3>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>



    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.js" integrity="sha256-2Kok7MbOyxpgUVvAk/HJ2jigOSYS2auK4Pfzbm7uH60="
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>

</html>